divs: sighting detailswent into a store, noticed the lights in the sky above the parking lot. i assumed that it was a halloween thing, went inside, shopped for 1\2 hour, came back outside and saw it again. it have me chills. drive a mile and a half home and the lights are above my parking lot now. really creeped me out so i took video of it with my iphone. sent it to my girlfriend, she says it's the northern lights but that doesn't look like any tnl's that i've found online. i sent it to my dad and he said send it to you guys asap. when i came in the house it was still in the sky. my phone has been acting up since i took the video too. dads voice got really distorted a few times, was hearing weird beeps and boils on the line and my key board is having very bad lag time, that never happens with this phone.
